OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fdry evening with some late sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Outbreaks of heavy thundery
OL,8,Frain with a risk of hail, developing
OL,9,Fthrough the early hours.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,12,Foccasional rain, heavy and thundery
OL,13,Frain at times. Some drier spells of
OL,14,Fweather too. Warm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
