OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FSome
OL,6,Fmorning sunny spells Saturday but
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy, perhaps thundery,
OL,8,Frain spreading east in afternoon.
OL,9,FSunday and Monday see sunny spells and
OL,10,Fshowers, with a fresh southwesterly
OL,11,Fbreeze. Much cooler.
